-- U.S. Treasury Designates Bomb Maker With Ties to Al-Qaeda
-- B y   B r e n d a n   M u r r a y
-- 2013-06-06T15:30:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-06/u-s-treasury-designates-bomb-maker-with-ties-to-al-qaeda.html
The U.S. Treasury Department said in
a statement today it designated Abd-al-Hamid al-Masli for
terrorism sanctions for “acting on behalf” of al-Qaeda in the
manufacturing of improvised explosive devices.  He operates an electronics and explosives workshop in
 Pakistan , the Treasury said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brendan Murray in Washington at 
 brmurray@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
